CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2026


Key bindings
  m          Toggle shaders
  o          Change objects
  s			 toggle light movement
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  time spent: 2 hours


  Results:
Integer vs Float for color:
For both representations the FPS is generally within the range 4800-5000 FPS. There is not much difference with this one, it's the kind of thing the compiler is good at fixing.

If statement in color:
Now the FPS is hanging around 4900 FPS. Even just 1 if statement has noticably impacted the framerate, if statements are really inefficient to do on the graphics card.

